  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick skillet or griddle over medium heat.",
    "Toast the bread slices for 2-3 minutes on each side, or until lightly browned.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together the freshly ground pistachios and honey until well combined.",
    "Add the coconut oil to the bowl and mix until the pistachio mixture is smooth and creamy.",
    "Spread a generous amount of the pistachio mixture onto each toasted bread slice.",
    "Sprinkle a pinch of sea salt over the top of each slice.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve immediately."
